Package: mqttbot
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.17), libssl3 (>= 3.0.0)
Maintainer: beanieboi <ich@abwesend.com>
Description: MQTT data publisher for Home Assistant
 A Rust-based MQTT data publisher that periodically queries third-party APIs
 and publishes metrics to MQTT for Home Assistant integration.
 .
 This daemon runs as a systemd service and requires MQTT broker credentials
 and API credentials to be configured via environment variables.
